    <h4 id="splittingup">Splitting up the squad</h4>
    <p>
        As with any 50 man squad, there should be 10 subgroups.
        The issue here is that there are 6 areas requiring attention.
        I suggest sending 1 subgroup to <span style="color:rgb(255,242,0);">North</span> and designate 1 to defend <span style="color:rgb(171,205,50);">Base Camp</span>. The other thumpers should all get 2 subgroups.
        When a side event comes, the thumpers with two subgroups should send one of their subs to the side event.
    </p>
    <h4 id="sideevents">Side Events</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <h5>Titanspawn Sapper</h5>
            <p>
                The sapper steals essence from the <span style="color:rgb(171,205,50);">main camp thumper</span>.
                <figure style="width:50px;float:inline-start;clear:none;">
                    <image src="/images/JW/Shared/Sniffa.png" alt="Sniffa" style="width:100%;"/>
                    <figcaption>Sniffa</figcaption>
                </figure>
                Track it down with your warclaw's Sniff skill.
                Break the sappers defiance bar to ping it on the map for everyone.
                Upon dying, it drops a ton of essence. Bring everyone that's available so you can feed it all back to the thumper.
            </p>
            
            <!--<image src="" alt="Titanspawn Sapper" style="width:100%;max-width:500px;"></image><br>-->
            <figure style="max-width:500px;">
                <image src="/images/JW/Thumper/SapperEssence.png" alt="Sapper essence" style="width:100%;"/>
                <figcaption>Sappers and Leaders drop a ton of essence.</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h5>Titanspawn Leaders</h5>
            <p>During the thumper phase, one of three Titanspawn Leaders will spawn.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h5 style="color:rgb(0,242,255);">Northwest Titanspawn Leader</h5>
                    <p>
                        Starts at <span style="color:rgb(0,242,255);">Stormsinger's Court</span>.
                        Walks south to the <span style="color:rgb(237,28,36);">West Thumper</span>.
                        Continues on to the <span style="color:rgb(171,205,50);">Main Camp</span>.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h5 style="color:rgb(145,82,255);">North Titanspawn Leader</h5>
                    <p>
                        Starts at <span style="color:rgb(145,82,255);">Steamshrieker's Court</span>.
                        Walks west through the tunnel to the <span style="color:rgb(0,162,232);">Center Thumper</span>.
                        Continues on to the <span style="color:rgb(171,205,50);">Main Camp</span>.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h5 style="color:rgb(244,255,60);">Southeast Titanspawn Leader</h5>
                    <p>
                        Starts at <span style="color:rgb(244,255,60);">Blightbringer's Court</span>.
                        Walks west to the <span style="color:rgb(255,127,39);">Southeast Thumper</span>.
                        Continues on to the <span style="color:rgb(171,205,50);">Main Camp</span>.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Once the Titanspawn Leader is defeated, Distant Memory will create several projections around the map.
                Collect the essence the leader dropped and turn it in to the nearest projection!
            </p>
            <figure>
                <image src="/images/JW/Thumper/ThumperTSLeaders.png" alt="TitanspawnLeaderRoutes" style="width:100%;max-width:800px;"/>
                <figcaption></figcaption>
            </figure>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h4 id="weather">Weather</h4>
