                <image src="/images/JW/Thumper/Sandswirl.png" alt="Sandswirl" style="width:100%;max-width:500px;"></image>
                <figcaption>A sandswirl </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h5>Snowstorm</h5>
            <span style="color:rgb(0,162,232);">Blizzard</span> - Ice formations fall on the ground, damaging and chilling.<br>
            <span style="color:rgb(153,217,234);">Snowballs</span> roll down the mountain.<br>
            <figure>
                <image src="/images/JW/Thumper/Snowstorm.png" alt="Snowball and Blizzard" style="width:100%;max-width:500px;"/>
            </figure>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h5>Thunderstorm</h5>
            Lightning Strikes - Lightning hits all over the mountain.<br>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h5>Volcano</h5>
